file.name: sentry_openapi3_spec.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 0.1.0
  title: Sentry API
  description: Sentry API
paths:
  /api/0/projects/:
    parameters:
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/AuthorizationHeader"
    get:
      operationId: GET /api/0/projects/
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                items:
                  properties:
                    avatar:
                      properties:
                        avatarType:
                          type: string
                      type: object
                    color:
                      type: string
                    dateCreated:
                      type: string
                    features:
                      items:
                        type: string
                      type: array
                    firstEvent:
                      type: string
                    hasAccess:
                      type: boolean
                    id:
                      type: string
                    isBookmarked:
                      type: boolean
                    isInternal:
                      type: boolean
                    isMember:
                      type: boolean
                    isPublic:
                      type: boolean
                    name:
                      type: string
                    organization:
                      properties:
                        avatar:
                          properties:
                            avatarType:
                              type: string
                          type: object
                        dateCreated:
                          type: string
                        features:
                          items:
                            type: string
                          type: array
                        id:
                          type: string
                        isEarlyAdopter:
                          type: boolean
                        name:
                          type: string
                        require2FA:
                          type: boolean
                        slug:
                          type: string
                          x-akita-type-hint: organization_slug
                        status:
                          properties:
                            id:
                              type: string
                            name:
                              type: string
                          type: object
                      type: object
                    slug:
                      type: string
                      x-akita-type-hint: project_slug
                    status:
                      type: string
                  type: object
                type: array
  /api/0/projects/{organization_slug}/{project_slug}/keys/:
    parameters:
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/AuthorizationHeader"
    get:
      operationId: GET /api/0/{organization_slug}/{project_slug}/keys/
      parameters:
        - name: organization_slug
          required: true
          in: path
          x-akita-type-hint: organization_slug
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: project_slug
          required: true
          in: path
          x-akita-type-hint: project_slug
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                items:
                  properties:
                    browserSdk:
                      properties:
                        choices:
                          items:
                            items:
                              type: string
                            type: array
                          type: array
                      type: object
                    browserSdkVersion:
                      type: string
                    dateCreated:
                      type: string
                    dsn:
                      properties:
                        cdn:
                          type: string
                        csp:
                          type: string
                        minidump:
                          type: string
                        public:
                          type: string
                        secret:
                          type: string
                        security:
                          type: string
                        unreal:
                          type: string
                      type: object
                    id:
                      type: string
                    isActive:
                      type: boolean
                    label:
                      type: string
                    name:
                      type: string
                    projectId:
                      format: int64
                      type: integer
                    public:
                      type: string
                      x-akita-type-hint: sentry_key
                    secret:
                      type: string
                  type: object
                type: array
  /api/1/store/:
    parameters:
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/AuthorizationHeader"
    post:
      operationId: POST /api/1/store/
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: sentry_key
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            x-akita-type-hint: sentry_key
        - in: query
          name: sentry_version
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            enum:
              - 7
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              properties:
                culprit:
                  type: string
                  x-akita-free-arg: true
                dist:
                  type: string
                  x-akita-free-arg: true
                environment:
                  type: string
                  x-akita-free-arg: true
                event_id:
                  type: string
                  x-akita-type-hint: event_id
                  x-akita-free-arg: true
                exception:
                  properties:
                    values:
                      items:
                        properties:
                          module:
                            type: string
                            x-akita-free-arg: true
                          type:
                            type: string
                            x-akita-free-arg: true
                          value:
                            type: string
                            x-akita-free-arg: true
                        required:
                          - type
                          - value
                          - module
                        type: object
                      type: array
                  required:
                    - values
                  type: object
                fingerprint:
                  items:
                    type: string
                    x-akita-free-arg: true
                  type: array
                level:
                  type: string
                  x-akita-free-arg: true
                logger:
                  type: string
                  x-akita-free-arg: true
                message:
                  type: string
                  x-akita-free-arg: true
                platform:
                  type: string
                  enum:
                    - as3
                    - c
                    - cfml
                    - cocoa
                    - csharp
                    - elixir
                    - haskell
                    - go
                    - groovy
                    - java
                    - javascript
                    - native
                    - node
                    - objc
                    - other
                    - perl
                    - php
                    - python
                    - ruby
                  x-akita-free-arg: true
                release:
                  type: string
                  x-akita-free-arg: true
                server_name:
                  type: string
                  x-akita-free-arg: true
                timestamp:
                  type: string
                  format: time
                  x-akita-free-arg: true
                transaction:
                  type: string
                  x-akita-free-arg: true
                user:
                  properties:
                    email:
                      type: string
                      format: email
                      x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                      x-akita-type-hint: user_email
                      x-akita-free-arg: true
                    id:
                      type: string
                      x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                      x-akita-type-hint: user_id
                      x-akita-free-arg: true
                    ip_address:
                      type: string
                      x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                      x-akita-type-hint: user_ip_address
                      x-akita-free-arg: true
                    username:
                      type: string
                      x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                      x-akita-type-hint: user_username
                      x-akita-free-arg: true
                    subscription:
                      type: string
                      x-akita-free-arg: true
                  required:
                    - email
                    - id
                    - ip_address
                    - username
                  type: object
              required:
                - timestamp
                - event_id
                - logger
                - platform
              type: object
        required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  id:
                    type: string
                type: object
  /api/0/projects/{organization_slug}/{project_slug}/events/:
    parameters:
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/AuthorizationHeader"
    get:
      operationId: GET /api/0/{organization_slug}/{project_slug}/events/
      parameters:
        - name: organization_slug
          required: true
          in: path
          x-akita-type-hint: organization_slug
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: project_slug
          required: true
          in: path
          x-akita-type-hint: project_slug
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                items:
                  properties:
                    culprit:
                      type: string
                    dateCreated:
                      type: string
                    event.type:
                      type: string
                    eventID:
                      type: string
                    groupID:
                      type: string
                    id:
                      type: string
                    message:
                      type: string
                    platform:
                      type: string
                    projectID:
                      type: string
                    tags:
                      items:
                        properties:
                          key:
                            type: string
                          value:
                            type: string
                        type: object
                      type: array
                    title:
                      type: string
                    user:
                      properties:
                        data:
                          properties:
                            subscription:
                              type: string
                          type: object
                        email:
                          type: string
                          x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                          x-akita-type-hint: user_email
                        id:
                          type: string
                          x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                          x-akita-type-hint: user_id
                        ip_address:
                          type: string
                          x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                          x-akita-type-hint: user_ip_address
                        username:
                          type: string
                          x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                          x-akita-type-hint: user_username
                      type: object
                  type: object
                type: array
  /api/0/projects/{organization_slug}/{project_slug}/users/:
    parameters:
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/AuthorizationHeader"
    get:
      operationId: GET /api/0/projects/{organization_slug}/{project_slug}/users/
      parameters:
        - name: organization_slug
          required: true
          in: path
          x-akita-type-hint: organization_slug
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: project_slug
          required: true
          in: path
          x-akita-type-hint: project_slug
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                items:
                  properties:
                    avatarUrl:
                      type: string
                    dateCreated:
                      type: string
                    email:
                      type: string
                      x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                      x-akita-type-hint: user_email
                    hash:
                      type: string
                    id:
                      type: string
                      x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                      x-akita-type-hint: user_id
                    identifier:
                      type: string
                    ipAddress:
                      type: string
                      x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                      x-akita-type-hint: user_ip_address
                    name:
                      type: string
                      x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                      x-akita-type-hint: user_name
                    tagValue:
                      type: string
                    username:
                      type: string
                      x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                      x-akita-type-hint: user_username
                  type: object
                type: array
  /api/0/projects/{organization_slug}/{project_slug}/issues/:
    parameters:
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/AuthorizationHeader"
    get:
      operationId: GET /api/0/projects/{organization_slug}/{project_slug}/issues/
      parameters:
        - name: organization_slug
          required: true
          in: path
          x-akita-type-hint: organization_slug
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: project_slug
          required: true
          in: path
          x-akita-type-hint: project_slug
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                items:
                  properties:
                    count:
                      type: string
                    culprit:
                      type: string
                    firstSeen:
                      type: string
                    hasSeen:
                      type: boolean
                    id:
                      type: string
                      x-akita-type-hint: issue_id
                    isBookmarked:
                      type: boolean
                    isPublic:
                      type: boolean
                    isSubscribed:
                      type: boolean
                    lastSeen:
                      type: string
                    level:
                      type: string
                    logger:
                      type: string
                    metadata:
                      properties:
                        type:
                          type: string
                        value:
                          type: string
                      type: object
                    numComments:
                      format: int64
                      type: integer
                    permalink:
                      type: string
                    platform:
                      type: string
                    project:
                      properties:
                        id:
                          type: string
                        name:
                          type: string
                        slug:
                          type: string
                          x-akita-type-hint: project_slug
                      type: object
                    shortId:
                      type: string
                    stats:
                      properties:
                        24h:
                          items:
                            items:
                              format: int64
                              type: integer
                            type: array
                          type: array
                      type: object
                    status:
                      type: string
                    statusDetails:
                      type: object
                    title:
                      type: string
                    type:
                      type: string
                    userCount:
                      format: int64
                      type: integer
                  type: object
                type: array
  /api/0/issues/{issue_id}/events/:
    parameters:
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/AuthorizationHeader"
    get:
      operationId: GET /api/0/issues/{issue_id}/events/
      parameters:
        - name: issue_id
          required: true
          in: path
          x-akita-type-hint: issue_id
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                items:
                  properties:
                    culprit:
                      type: string
                    dateCreated:
                      type: string
                    event.type:
                      type: string
                    eventID:
                      type: string
                    groupID:
                      type: string
                    id:
                      type: string
                    message:
                      type: string
                    platform:
                      type: string
                    projectID:
                      type: string
                    tags:
                      items:
                        properties:
                          key:
                            type: string
                          value:
                            type: string
                        type: object
                      type: array
                    title:
                      type: string
                    user:
                      properties:
                        data:
                          properties:
                            subscription:
                              type: string
                          type: object
                        email:
                          type: string
                          x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                          x-akita-type-hint: user_email
                        id:
                          type: string
                          x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                          x-akita-type-hint: user_id
                        ip_address:
                          type: string
                          x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                          x-akita-type-hint: user_ip_address
                        username:
                          type: string
                          x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                          x-akita-type-hint: user_username
                      type: object
                  type: object
                type: array
  /api/0/projects/{organization_slug}/{project_slug}/user-feedback/:
    parameters:
      - $ref: "#/components/parameters/AuthorizationHeader"
    post:
      operationId: POST /api/0/projects/{organization_slug}/{project_slug}/user-feedback/
      parameters:
        - name: organization_slug
          required: true
          in: path
          x-akita-type-hint: organization_slug
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: project_slug
          required: true
          in: path
          x-akita-type-hint: project_slug
          schema:
            type: string
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              properties:
                comments:
                  type: string
                  x-akita-free-arg: true
                email:
                  type: string
                  format: email
                  x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                  x-akita-type-hint: user_email
                  x-akita-free-arg: true
                event_id:
                  type: string
                  x-akita-type-hint: event_id
                  x-akita-free-arg: true
                name:
                  type: string
                  x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                  x-akita-type-hint: user_name
                  x-akita-free-arg: true
              required:
                - event_id
                - name
                - comments
                - email
              type: object
        required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  comments:
                    type: string
                  dateCreated:
                    type: string
                  email:
                    type: string
                    x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                    x-akita-type-hint: user_email
                  event:
                    properties:
                      eventID:
                        type: string
                        x-akita-type-hint: event_id
                      id:
                        type: string
                    type: object
                  eventID:
                    type: string
                    x-akita-type-hint: event_id
                  id:
                    type: string
                  name:
                    type: string
                    x-akita-is-sensitive: true
                    x-akita-type-hint: user_name
                type: object
servers:
  - url: http://localhost:9000
components:
  parameters:
    AuthorizationHeader:
      name: Authorization
      in: header
      description: "Auth token used to identify and authorize API caller"
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
        enum:
          - "Bearer 8f2c1206259843399b0e5cbaadb610d49b52b60a18ba4e21898b9375fbd6ee07"
        x-akita-free-arg: true
        x-akita-is-sensitive: true
